tract%20from%20the%20state%20government's%20failures.%20In%20a%20sharp%20attack%20of%20his%20own%2C%20Thackeray%20junior%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20a%20Manipur%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSadly%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20cannot%20govern...%20they%20resort%20to%20violence%20and%20riots.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20Manipur...%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20they%20want%20to%20convert%20Maharashtra%20to.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20dig%20up%20the%20history%20of%20someone%20who%20lived%20over%20300%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20speak%20about%20the%20future...%20the%20present.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20irony%20is%20the%20grave%20is%20protected%20by%20the%20central%20government...%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouses%20and%20shops%20were%20vandalised%2C%20vehicles%20were%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20and%20nearly%2040%20people%20injured%20in%20violence%20that%20erupted%20Monday%20starting%207.30%20pm%2C%20reportedly%20after%20hardline%20group%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20burnt%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20Mughal%20ruler%20wrapped%20in%20a%20green%20cloth%20to%20'symbolise%20his%20grave'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20this%20was%20a%20rumour%20-%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20-%20and%20the%20VHP%20protesters%20had%20only%20burnt%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbolic%20grave%20with%20bundles%20of%20grass%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20rumour%20was%20spread%2C%20around%20250%20Muslims%20arrived%20at%20the%20VHP's%20protest%20site%20and%20threatened%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20said%20they%20would%20set%20vehicles%20on%20fire%2C%20police%20used%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%20Maharashtra's%20junior%20Home%20Minister%2C%20Yogesh%20Kadam%2C%20said%2047%20people%20have%20been%20detained%20so%20far.%20He%20said%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20cops%20and%20two%20civilians%20ha