at%20the%20project%20will%20look%20like%20is%20still%20a%20mystery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELegacy%20and%20new%20defense%20companies%20are%20vying%20for%20opportunities%20within%20the%20'Golden%20Dome'%20initiative.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20have%20been%20arguments%20for%20the%20project%20to%20focus%20on%20a%20range%20of%20threats%20beyond%20missiles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20envisions%20his%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Dome%20for%20America%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20next-generation%20missile%20shield%2C%20but%20defense%20companies%20see%20other%20opportunities%20amid%20the%20heightened%20focus%20on%20fending%20off%20threats%20to%20the%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20exactly%20the%20project%20will%20entail%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20but%20industry%20partners%20are%20curious%20to%20see%20if%20it%20will%20include%20less%20conventional%20systems%20like%20counter-drone%20capabilities%20and%20electronic%20warfare.%20The%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Dome%26quot%3B%20effort%20is%20being%20eyed%20closely%20by%20legacy%20defense%20companies%20and%20smaller%2C%20younger%20companies%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELockheed%20Martin%2C%20an%20established%20player%20in%20integrated%20missile%20defense%2C%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bready%20to%20answer%20the%20call.%26quot%3B%20Other%20big%20defense%20companies%2C%20like%20RTX%20and%20Northrop%20Grumman%2C%20have%20also%20shown%20their%20interest%20in%20the%20project.%20But%20other%20defense%20firms%20want%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20action%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlueHalo%2C%20a%20Virginia-based%20defense%20contractor%2C%20has%20said%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20already%20set%20to%20be%20a%20massive%20undertaking%20as%20the%20Trump%20administration%20effectively%20revives%20the%20Reagan-era%20Strategic%20Defense%20Initiative%2C%20will%20ultimately%20require%20%26quot%3Bthe%20full%20might%20of%20the%20Defense%20Industrial%20Base%20to%20achieve%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20BlueHalo%20CEO%20Jonathan%20Moneymaker%20said%20that%20a%20comprehensive%20Golden%20Dome%20could%20become%20an%20all-encompassing%20threat%20response%20with%20buy-in%20from%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20defense%20tech%20and%20AI%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlueHalo%20develops%20cost-effective%20counter-drone%20systems%2C%20among%20other%20defense%20technologies.%20The%20company%20developed%20the%20Palletized%20High%20Energy%20Laser%20system%20that%20uses%20directed%20energy%20and%20AI%20to%20eliminate%20drones%20for%20the%20Army%20and%20is%20working%20on%20a%20next-generation%20counter-drone%20missile%20that%20it%20recently%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6a8375b-0a5c-422c-be70-5b4e4f12347c%5C%22%3E'A%20very%20wide%20swath%20of%20threat%20vectors'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMoneymaker%20said%20the%20defense%20industry%20will%20need%20greater%20clarity%20for%20companies%20to%20begin%20fielding%20potential%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Dome%26quot%3B%20solutions.%20Right%20now%2C%20there%20are%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20the%20scale%20and%20how%20extensive%20the%20White%20House%20wants%20this%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20are%20not%20the%20only%20uncertainties.%20Agencies%20like%20NORTHCOM%2C%20Space%20Command%2C%20and%20the%20Missile%20Defense%20Agency%20may%20all%20have%20requirements%20and%20varying%20levels%20of%20ownership%2C%20raising%20responsibility%20questions.%20Leading%20agencies%20will%20also%20have%20to%20hash%20out%20how%20the%20potential%20inclusion%20of%20electronic%20warfare%20and%20signals%20intelligence%20will%20work%20on%20American%20soil%20and%20balance%20citizens'%20privacy%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Standard%20Missile-6%20Dual%20II%20is%20launched%20from%20the%20USS%20Daniel%20Inouye%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Missile%20Range%20Facility%20in%20Kauai%2C%20Hawaii%20as%20part%20of%20testing%20event%2C%20March%2030%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d88751b8b41a9673fae489%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Standard%20Missile-6%20Dual%20II%20is%20launched%20from%20the%20USS%20Daniel%20Inouye%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Missile%20Range%20Facility%20in%20Kauai%2C%20Hawaii%20as%20part%20of%20testing%20event%2C%20March%2030%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EMark%20Wright%2FMissile%20Defense%20Agency%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20issues%20are%20likely%20being%20addressed%20now%20as%20the%20first%20planning%20deadline%20fast%20approaches.%20In%20late%20January%2C%20the%20White%20House%20gave%20the%20Pentagon%2060%20days%20from%20the%20president's%20executive%20order%20to%20develop%20a%20plan%20for%20the%20new%20shield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20order%20for%20what%20Trump%20initially%20called%20%26quot%3BIron%20Dome%20for%20America%26quot%3B%20was%20focused%20on%20the%20threat%20of%20ballistic%2C%20hypersonic%2C%20and%20advanced%20cruise%20missiles.%20But%20it%20also%20mentioned%20without%20specificity%20%26quot%3Bother%20next-generation%20aerial%20attacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20clarity%20on%20whether%20it%20would%20want%20the%20new%20project%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20than%20missile%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoneymaker%20said%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20dangers%20the%20US%20is%20facing%2C%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20varying%20degrees%20of%20technology%20that%20are%20ranging%20from%20very%20unsophisticated%20threats%20to%20very%2C%20very%20sophisticated%20threats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20potential%20threats%20include%20everything%20from%20complex%20and%20maneuverable%20hypersonic%20missiles%20to%20cheap%2C%20off-the-shelf%20drones%20with%20munitions%20taped%20to%20them.%20The%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20seen%20the%20revolutionary%20employment%20of%20drones%20and%20loitering%20munitions.%20The%20threats%20to%20the%20nation%20can%20range%20from%20missiles%20to%20cyberattacks%20to%20drone%20swarms.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20very%20wide%20swath%20of%20threat%20vectors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20military%20officials%20have%20argued%20the%20original%20focus%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20shield%20project%20was%20too%20narrowly%20focused%20on%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlen%20VanHerck%2C%20a%20retired%20Air%20Force%20General%20who%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20head%20of%20NORAD%2C%20and%20Pete%20Fesler%2C%20another%20retired%20Air%20Force%20general%20and%20former%20NORAD%20official%2C%20argued%20last%20month%20in%20The%20National%20Interest%20that%20plans%20for%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Dome%26quot%3B%20are%20stuck%20in%20a%20bygone%20era%20focused%20primarily%20on%20legacy%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20military%20officials%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Ba%20comprehensive%20and%20holistic%20approach%20to%20homeland%20defense%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20addresses%20the%20full%20spectrum%20of%20current%20and%20future%20threats.%26quot%3B%20That%20approach%20could%20include%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20cyber-resilience%2C%20and%20improved%20counter-drone%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Pentagon%20cannot%20afford%20to%20simply%20buy%20more%20of%20yesterday.%20Instead%2C%20it%20must%20dynamically%20adapt%20for%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20a%20fully%20operational%20Iron%20Dome%20within%20the%20US%20will%20be%20a%20heavy%20lift%2C%20one%20that%20demands%20organization%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhole%20of%20government%26quot%3B%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20clearly%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20across%20a%20lot%20of%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20Moneymaker%20said.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20government%20and%20industry%20alike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%2