rs%20and%20developers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20going%20to%20certify%20any%20institution%20as%20bad%20or%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%2C%20who%20was%20heading%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20hearing%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20definitely%20have%20CBI%20probe.%20That%20is%20clear.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20are%20crying.%20We%20can't%20wipe%20their%20tears%20but%20we%20can%20address%20their%20issues.%20Something%20very%20effective%20has%20to%20be%20done%20in%20timebound%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20The%20Central%20agency%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20file%20a%20plan%20on%20how%20it%20intends%20to%20tackle%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20ruling%20in%20July%202024%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20that%20no%20coercive%20action%2C%20including%20EMI%20recovery%2C%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20homebuyers%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20who%20haven't%20received%20possession%20of%20their%20flats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20order%20is%20far%20from%20being%20implemented.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20homeowners%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20loan%20amounts%20were%20illegally%20disbursed%20directly%20into%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20builders%2Fdevelopers%20in%20violation%20of%20RBI%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20alleged%20that%20the%20homebuyers%20were%20used%20as%20a%20medium%20to%20get%20the%20loans%20sanctioned.%20When%20the%20buyers%20objected%2C%20the%20banks%20initiated%20action%20against%20them%2C%20it%20has%20been%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20not%20certify%20a%20single%20bank%20free%20from%20doubt...we%20have%20seen%20their%20functioning...you%20see%20the%20conduct%20of%20public%20institutions!%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kant%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20financers%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20particular%20builder%20goes%20insolvent%2C%20it's%20not%20my%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kant%20shot%20back%2C%20%26quot%3BYour%20%C2%A0%20fault%20is%20that%20knowing%20not%20a%20brick%20has%20been%20laid%20at%20the%20site%2C%20you%20released%2060%20per%20cent!%20How%20can%20this%20be%20without%20quid%20pro%20quo!%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20suggested%20that%20the%20banks%20can%20refrain%20from%20charging%20interest%20till%20possession%20is%20given.%20But%20the%20court%20shot%20it%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20going%20to%20address%20the%20larger%20issue.%20It%20is%20not%20going%20to%20heal%20the%20ailment%20the%20entire%20system%20is%20suffering%20from.%20Lakhs%2C%20lakhs%20of%20people...%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20handling%20the%20poor%20people's%20plight%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20any%20reluctance.%20We%20want%20to%20go%20into%20the%20root...%20we%20have%20zero%20tolerance.%20We%20will%20request%20the%20amicus%20(curiae)%20to%20assist%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20decided%20to%20appoint%20an%20amicus%20curiae%20since%20the%20volume%20of%20such%20cases%20is%20huge.%20The%20next%20hearing%20will%20be%20held%20after%20two%20weeks.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742299740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F0vu7p2oo_gurugram-apartment-generic_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthousands-crying-supreme-court-talks-of-cbi-probe-into-homeowners-troubles-7951862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20alleged%20nexus%20between%20banks%20and%20builders%20and%20assured%20that%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20will%20be%20held%20into%20the%20grievances%20of%20homeowners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthousands-crying-supreme-court-talks-of-cbi-probe-into-homeowners-troubles-7951862%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Haryana%20To%20NASA%3A%20Remembering%20Indian-Origin%20Astronaut%20Kalpana%20Chawla%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20on%20her%20way%20to%20Earth%20after%20an%20extended%20nine-month%20stay%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS).%20On%20this%20monumental%20occasion%2C%20the%20world%20remembers%20Kalpana%20Chawla%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20has%20inspired%20not%20only%20Ms%20Williams%20but%20many%20others%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chawla%2C%20who%20would%20have%20turned%2062%20this%20year%2C%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20go%20to%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Karnal%2C%20Haryana%2C%20on%20March%2017%2C%201962%2C%20Kalpana%20Chawla%20was%20fascinated%20by%20aeroplanes%20and%20space%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20Encouraged%20by%20her%20family%2C%20she%20pursued%20her%20passion%20by%20earning%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20aeronautical%20engineering%20from%20Punjab%20Engineering%20College.%20She%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20obtaining%20a%20Master's%20degree%20in%20aerospace%20engineering%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20in%201984%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20PhD%20in%20the%20same%20subject%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20in%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20academic%20excellence%20and%20determination%20took%20her%20to%20NASA%20in%201994.%20By%201997%2C%20she%20had%20achieved%20what%20no%20other%20Indian%20woman%20had%20before%20-%20she%20became%20an%20astronaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpana%20Chawla%20went%20on%20two%20space%20missions%20that%20cemented%20her%20place%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20first%20mission%2C%20STS-87%20in%201997%2C%20was%20aboard%20the%20Space%20Shuttle%20Columbia%2C%20where%20she%20served%20as%20a%20mission%20specialist%20and%20robotic%20arm%20operator.%20This%20journey%20made%20her%20the%20first%20woman%20of%20Indian%20origin%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20mission%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Inder%20Kumar%20Gujral%20spoke%20to%20Ms%20Chawla%20while%20she%20was%20in%20space%2C%20telling%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BKalpana%2C%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20you.%20Each%20one%20of%20us%20in%20India%20is%20proud%20of%20a%20person%20like%20you%2C%20who%20has%20done%20such%20pioneering%20work%2C%20particularly%20the%20women%20and%20youth%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chawla%20described%20space%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20dome%20of%20a%20dark%20sky%20and%20stars%20everywhere...%20very%20much%20like%20a%20storybook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20her%20experience%20of%20seeing%20India%20from%20space%20with%20the%20late%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%2C%20we%20picked%20a%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20from%20the%20orbiter...%20The%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20is%20so%20magnificent%20that%20it%20really%20belongs%20to%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDHdjx6Rv0qZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDHdjx6Rv0qZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDHdjx6Rv0qZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2