inters.%20Their%20answer%20was%20straightforward%3A%20medical%20education%20in%20Russia%20was%20far%20more%20affordable%2C%20the%20hospital%20training%20was%20solid%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20their%20degrees%20were%20recognised%20back%20in%20India.%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20admire%20their%20determination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20interpreter%20on%20that%20trip%20was%20a%20naturalised%20Russian%20citizen%2C%20originally%20from%20Kerala.%20His%20father%2C%20a%20staunch%20Leftist%2C%20had%20sent%20him%20to%20study%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%20the%20late%201980s%E2%80%94not%20for%20the%20academics%2C%20but%20for%20ideological%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20master's%20in%20Russian%20literature%2C%20met%20my%20wife%20here%20and%20now%20we%20have%20a%20beautiful%20daughter.%20No%20regrets.%E2%80%9D%20No%20wonder%20he%20was%20so%20fluent%20in%20Russian%E2%80%94not%20to%20mention%20his%20penchant%20for%20vodka%20and%20caviar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20hundreds%20of%20Indian%20students%20like%20him%20enrolled%20in%20Soviet%20universities%2C%20with%20many%20eventually%20settling%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia%2C%20On%20Old%20Study%20Destination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20never%20been%20an%20unknown%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students.%20Their%20numbers%20have%20been%20steady%2C%20never%20overwhelming.%20But%20now%20the%20trend%20is%20changing%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20figures%20presented%20in%20Parliament%20recently%20tell%20a%20different%20story%3A%20Indian%20students%20are%20increasingly%20looking%20beyond%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Four%26quot%3B%E2%80%94the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%20and%20Australia%E2%80%94once%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20international%20education.%20The%20tide%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20is%20turning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%2C%20once%20a%20hot%20favourite%20for%20Indian%20students%2C%20took%20a%20massive%20hit%20in%202024%E2%80%94enrolments%20from%20India%20plunged%20by%2041%25.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Russia%20saw%20a%2034%25%20spike%2C%20drawing%20in%20more%20Indian%20students%20than%20the%20previous%20year.%20The%20UK%20also%20felt%20the%20squeeze%E2%80%94Indian%20student%20numbers%20dropped%20from%20136%2C921%20in%202023%20to%2098%2C890%20in%202024%2C%20a%20sharp%2028%25%20decline%20in%20just%20one%20year.%20The%20US%20and%20Australia%20didn't%20escape%20the%20slump%20either%2C%20with%20significant%20drops%20in%20Indian%20student%20enrolments.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20this%20isn't%20true%20only%20of%20Indian%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20global%20student%20mobility%20is%20also%20taking%20a%20hit.%20International%20education%20is%20a%20%24200%20billion%20industry%2C%20with%20the%20UK%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%20and%20Australia%20being%20its%20biggest%20players.%20But%20across%20the%20board%2C%20numbers%20are%20sliding.%20Canada%20saw%20a%2027%25%20drop%20in%20total%20international%20enrolments%2C%20while%20the%20UK%20reported%20an%2018%25%20decline.%20The%20US%20took%20a%20smaller%20but%20notable%20hit%2C%20with%20a%206%25%20dip%20in%20international%20student%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESigns%20of%20trouble%20keep%20piling%20up.%20ApplyBoard%2C%20a%20global%20university%20application%20portal%20used%20by%20over%20a%20million%20students%20from%20150%20countries%2C%20confirmed%20the%20downward%20trend%20in%20its%20latest%20study.%20Search%20interest%20for%20the%20Big%20Four%20study%20destinations%20fell%20by%2014%25%20in%20the%20year%20ending%20January%202025%2C%20following%20an%20even%20steeper%2022%25%20drop%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20September%2C%20alarm%20bells%20were%20ringing%20across%20the%20Big%20Four%20study%20destinations.%20Worried%20educators%20and%20university%20leaders%20gathered%20in%20London%20for%20a%20crisis%20summit%2C%20grappling%20with%20the%20freefall%20in%20international%20student%20numbers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20that%20the%20US%20and%20the%20foreign%20market%20can%20continue%20to%20dominate%20is%20a%20very%20old%20framework%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr.%20Fanta%20Aw%2C%20CEO%20of%20NAFSA%3A%20Association%20of%20International%20Educators.%20The%20overriding%20feeling%20was%20that%20the%20landscape%20was%20shifting%20and%20students%20were%20looking%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Big%20Four%20were%20once%20an%20unshakable%20education%20powerhouse%2C%20so%20too%20were%20the%20outbound%20students%20from%20China%2C%20India%20and%20South%20Korea%E2%80%94together%2C%20nearly%20two%20million%20of%20them%20fuelling%20the%20financial%20engine%20of%20Western%20universities.%20But%20as%20these%20students%20explore%20alternative%20destinations%2C%20the%20West's%20higher%20education%20sector%20faces%20a%20painful%20problem.%20Fewer%20students%20mean%20tighter%20budgets%2C%20struggling%20universities%20and%20a%20fading%20global%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20self-inflicted%20ones%2C%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20declining%20number%20of%20foreign%20students%20in%20the%20Big%20Four%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHostile%20Rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20length%20of%20student%20visas%2C%20governments%20in%20these%20countries%20are%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20graduates%20to%20stay%20and%20work.%20The%20UK's%20crackdown%20on%20dependent%20visas%2C%20Canada's%20cap%20on%20study%20permits%2C%20and%20Australia's%20tougher%20rules%20on%20post-study%20work%20have%20made%20it%20harder%20for%20students%20to%20justify%20the%20investment.%20The%20universities%20say%20the%20government%20actions%20are%20counterproductive%2C%20but%20their%20protests%20are%20royally%20disregarded.%20By%20March%2012%2C%20President%20Trump%20had%20signed%20128%20executive%20orders%2C%20including%2010%20targeting%20immigration%E2%80%94one%20of%20which%20called%20for%20a%20sweeping%20review%20of%20all%20visa%20programmes%2C%20including%20those%20for%20international%20students.%C2%A0A%20survey%20found%20that%20any%20US%20travel%20ban%20on%20students%20or%20visitors%20could%20deal%20a%20serious%20blow%20to%20the%20country's%20reputation%20as%20a%20study%20destination.%20Nearly%20two-thirds%20of%20respondents%20said%20such%20a%20move%20would%20shatter%20their%20perception%20of%20the%20US%20as%20a%20welcoming%20place%20for%20international%20students%E2%80%94many%20would%20no%20longer%20even%20consider%20studying%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERising%20Costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudying%20in%20these%20countries%20has%20become%20increasingly%20expensive%2C%20especially%20with%20inflation%20pushing%20up%20rent%2C%20food%20and%20daily%20expenses.%20Many%20students%20are%20looking%20at%20cheaper%20yet%20high-quality%20alternatives%20like%20Russia%2C%20Central%20Asian%20countries%2C%20and%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeopolitical%20Tensions%20And%20Rise%20Of%20Non-Western%20Hubs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20xenophobia%2C%20racial%20attacks%20and%20political%20uncertainties%20are%20making%20students%20rethink%20their%20choices.%20Countries%20seen%20as%20more%20welcoming%20and%20politically%20stable%20are%20gaining%20traction%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERise%20of%20quality%20non-Western%20education%20hubs%3A%20Countries%20like%20China%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Singapore%20and%20Japan%20are%20aggressively%20expanding%20their%20universities%2C%20offering%20scholarships%20and%20partnering%20with%20global%20institutions%20to%20attract%20international%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20UK's%20Woes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20I've%20been%20reading%20reports%20for%20the%20past%20year%20warning%20that%20%26quot%3BBritish%20universities%20are%20in%20freefall%E2%80%9D.%20The%20crisis%20is%20real%E2%80%94universities%20are%20slashing%20jobs%20by%20the%20hundreds.%20In%20January%2C%20Bournemouth%20University%20announced%20400%20job%20cuts%E2%80%94a%20sign%20of%20just%20how%20deep%20the%20problem%20runs.%20Higher%20education%20in%20the%20UK%20is%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20a%20sinking%20ship.%20The%20number%20of%20international%20students%20is%20plummeting%2C%20and%20universities%20are%20staring%20down%20a%20serious%20funding%20crisis.%20According%20to%20British%20media%2C%20nearly%2080%25%20of%20institutions%20could%20soon%20be%20running%20deficits%20and%20many%20are%20already%20in%20survival%20mode%E2%80%94slashing%20jobs%2C%20shutting%20down%20courses%2C%20cutting%20back%20on%20catering%2C%20merging%20institutions%20and%20outsourcing%20services%20just%20to%20stay%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warning%20signs%20have%20been%20flashing%20for%20years%2C%20but%20things%20look%20set%20to%20get%20worse.%20Prospective%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20students%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20problems%2C%20and%20they%20are%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20by%20looking%20at%20other%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Crisis%20Across%20the%20Atlantic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20recently%20delivered%20a%20hard%20%24400%20million%20punch%20to%20Columbia%20University%2C%20pulling%20federal%20grants%20for%20allegedly%20failing%20to%20control%20anti-Semitism%20and%20%26quot%3Billegal%20protests%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20ironic%20that%20this%20is%20the%20same%20Columbia%20that%2C%20in%20April%202024%2C%20called%20in%20the%20police%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20a%20pro-Palestine%20student%20encampment%2C%20leading%20to%20over%20100%20students%20being%20arrested%2C%20some%20beaten%20up%20and%20a%20full-scale%20police%20raid%20on%20campus.%20Columbia's%20then-president%2C%20Minouche%20Shafik%2C%20had%20already%20promised%20a%20congressional%20committee%20that%20she'd%20crack%20down%20harder%20on%20student%20activism%E2%80%94but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20her%20loyalty%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20save%20the%20university%20from%20Trump's%20wrath.%20The%20moral%20of%20the%20story%3A%20Bending%20over%20backwards%20for%20political%20approval%20doesn't%20always%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20education%20purge%20is%20accelerating.%20Nearly%201%2C300%20employees%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20were%20recently%20fired%2C%20slashing%20its%20workforce%20to%20just%20over%202%2C100%20people%E2%80%94skeleton%20staff%20for%20a%20federal%20agency%20overseeing%20education%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20no%20mistake%2C%20the%20US%20remains%20a%20dream%20destination%20for%20many%2C%20but%20foreign%20students%E2%80%94including%20those%20from%20India%E2%80%94are%20turning%20away%20from%20the%20Big%20Four%20as%20political%20hostility%2C%20visa%20restrictions%20and%20funding%20cuts%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20welcome.%20Universities%2C%20long%20reliant%20on%20international%20tuition%20fees%2C%20now%20face%20financial%20uncertainty%2C%20while%20students%20rethink%20their%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742298240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fd167t2jg_student-generic-unsplash_625x300_20_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findian-students-are-fast-giving-up-on-their-american-dream-7951703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20students%20are%20increasingly%20looking%20beyond%20the%20'Big%20Four'%3A%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%20and%20Australia.%20But%20why%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findian-students-are-fast-giving-up-on-their-american-dream-7951703%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%