www.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcpq2pndw82jo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcpq2pndw82jo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20Highlights%20UN's%20Blunder%20On%20Kashmir%2C%20Calls%20For%20New%20World%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20injustice%20done%20by%20the%20West%20at%20the%20UN%20over%20Kashmir%20was%20highlighted%20at%20The%20Raisina%20Dialogue%20-%20a%20global%20multilateral%20conference%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%20each%20year.%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20did%20not%20mince%20his%20words%20as%20he%20showed%20how%20the%20United%20Nations%20had%20faltered%20in%20its%20understanding%20and%20approach%20to%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20noted%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Blongest-standing%26quot%3B%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20a%20territory%20globally%20after%20World%20War%20II%20has%20been%20experienced%20by%20India%20-%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20enitre%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20includes%20Gilgit%20and%20Baltistan%2C%20called%20Northern%20Areas%20before%201970%2C%20had%20acceded%20to%20India%20in%201947.%20Pakistan%2C%20in%20a%20unilateral%20act%20of%20aggression%2C%20invaded%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20has%20been%20illegally%20occupying%20parts%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Kashmir%20at%20the%20forum%20today%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20highlighted%20the%20selective%20approach%20and%20application%20of%20global%20rules%20on%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20raised%20concerns%20over%20historical%20injustices%20in%20dealing%20with%20certain%20issues%2C%20he%20batted%20for%20establishing%20a%20%26quot%3Breformed%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20fair%26quot%3B%20United%20Nations.%20Explaining%20how%20the%20UN%20had%20greatly%20erred%20in%20not%20condemning%20Pakistan's%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Battacker%26quot%3B%20(Pakistan)%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bvictim%26quot%3B%20(India)%20were%20clubbed%20under%20the%20same%20bracket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20speak%20of%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity.%20All%20of%20us%20agree%20that%20it%20is%20a%20vital%20principle.%20It's%20the%20bedrock%20of%20global%20rules.%20After%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20the%20longest%20standing%20illegal%2C%20I%20would%20say%20presence%2C%20occupation%20of%20a%20territory%20by%20another%20country%20pertains%20to%20India%2C%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20went%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20but%20what%20was%20an%20invasion%20was%20made%20into%20a%20dispute.%20So%20the%20attacker%20and%20the%20victim%20were%20put%20on%20par.%20Who%20were%20the%20culpable%20parties%3F%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Belgium%2C%20Australia%2C%20USA.%20So%2C%20pardon%20me%2C%20but%20I%20have%20some%20question%20marks%20on%20that%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacking%20a%20reformed%20and%20strong%20UN%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20global%20norms%20and%20rules%20must%20be%20applied%20uniformly.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20a%20strong%20UN%20but%20a%20strong%20UN%20requires%20a%20fair%20UN%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20strong%20global%20order%20must%20have%20some%20basic%20consistency%20of%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20new%20and%20reformed%20world%20order.%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20think%20we%20do%20need%20an%20international%20order%20just%20like%20we%20need%20a%20domestic%20order.%20Just%20like%20you%20need%20a%20society%20in%20a%20country%2C%20you%20need%20an%20international%20version%20of%20that%20and%20its%20not%20just%20big%20countries%20who%20will%20benefit%20if%20there%20is%20no%20order.%20I%20would%20argue%20that%20any%20country%20which%20would%20take%20risk%2C%20which%20would%2