l%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Devendra%20Fadnavis'%20'Chhaava'%20Mention%20In%20Assembly%20Address%20On%20Nagpur%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBlockbuster%20movie%20'Chhaava'%20brought%20the%20history%20of%20Maratha%20king%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%20to%20the%20fore%20and%20ignited%20public%20anger%20against%20Mughal%20ruler%20Aurangzeb%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20today%20while%20addressing%20the%20Assembly%20about%20the%20violence%20and%20arson%20in%20Nagpur%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20blame%20a%20movie.%20%26quot%3BChhaava%20brought%20the%20history%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%20before%20the%20people%20and%20their%20sentiments%20were%20ignited.%20Also%2C%20the%20public%20anger%20against%20Aurangzeb%20is%20coming%20to%20the%20fore.%20Keeping%20these%20things%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20law%20and%20order%20system%20must%20be%20maintained%20and%20everyone%20should%20be%20patient.%20If%20anyone%20riots%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action%20regardless%20of%20caste%20or%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaxman%20Utekar's%20Chhaava%20stars%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20as%20Maratha%20king%20Shambhaji%20Maharaj%20and%20Akshaye%20Khanna%20as%20Aurangzeb.%20The%20film%20portrays%20the%20Maratha%20king's%20battles%20against%20the%20Mughals%20and%20his%20subsequent%20capture%20and%20brutal%20execution.%20The%20film%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20massive%20hit%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20the%20violence%20in%20Nagpur%20%26quot%3Blooks%20like%20a%20well-planned%20attack%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Nagpur%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20held%20protests.%20Rumours%20were%20spread%20that%20things%20containing%20religious%20content%20were%20burnt...%20It%20looks%20like%20a%20well-planned%20attack.%20No%20one%20has%20permission%20to%20take%20law%2