the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20marble%20screens%20on%20three%20sides%20of%20the%20tomb%20were%20erected%20by%20the%20Nizams%20of%20Hyderabad%20later%2C%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20Lord%20Curzon%2C%20who%20served%20as%20viceroy%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fvg6l83v_aurangzeb_625x300_18_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Aurangzeb%20Told%20Sons%20About%20His%20Tomb%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20History%20of%20Aurangzib%20by%20Jadunath%20Sarkar%20cites%20an%20alleged%20will%20of%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20with%20detailed%20instructions%20on%20his%20final%20resting%20place.%20He%20allocated%20%26quot%3Bfour%20rupees%20and%20two%20annas%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20tomb%2C%20the%20price%20of%20caps%20he%20sewed%20himself%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20in%20his%20later%20years.%20He%20also%20said%20three%20hundred%20and%20five%20rupees%2C%20which%20he%20received%20as%20wages%20for%20copying%20the%20Quran%2C%20were%20in%20his%20purse.%20%26quot%3BDistribute%20them%20to%20the%20faqirs%20on%20the%20day%20of%20my%20death.%20As%20the%20money%20got%20by%20copying%20the%20Quran%20is%20regarded%20with%20respect%20by%20the%20Shia%20sect*%2C%20do%20not%20spend%20it%20on%20my%20shroud%20and%20other%20necessaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20will%20also%20instructed%20that%20the%20top%20of%20the%20coffin%20on%20his%20bier%20be%20covered%20with%20a%20coarse%20white%20cloth.%20It%20said%20the%20spreading%20of%20a%20canopy%20and%20any%20procession%20of%20musicians%20must%20be%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5fll8cp_aurangzeb-protest_625x300_18_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaharashtra%20and%20Aurangzeb%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20historical%20figures%2C%20Aurangzeb%20divides%20opinion.%20While%20many%20regard%20him%20as%20an%20intolerant%20ruler%20whose%20reign%20witnessed%20the%20destruction%20of%20many%20temples%2C%20others%20argue%20that%20politics%2C%20and%20not%20religious%20fanaticism%2C%20drove%20his%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20however%2C%20Aurangzeb%20is%20a%20villain.%20The%20Mughal%20emperor%20fought%20Marathas%20for%20about%20two%20decades%20and%20brutally%20executed%20Maratha%20king%20Sambhaji%2C%20son%20of%20Maratha%20icon%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20It%20was%20against%20this%20backdrop%20that%20Aurangabad%20was%20renamed%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajnagar%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20in%202022%20to%20honour%20the%20Maratha%20ruler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%20has%20come%20to%20be%20regarded%20as%20a%20martyr%2C%20with%20Hindu%20nationalists%20citing%20his%20bravery%20and%20loyalty%20to%20religion%20in%20the%20face%20of%20death.%20This%20narrative%20was%20reinforced%20by%20the%20blockbuster%20Chhava%2C%20a%20movie%20based%20on%20Sambhaji's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmotions%20ran%20high%2C%20and%20then%20a%20remark%20by%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA%20Abu%20Azmi%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Mr%20Azmi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20consider%20Aurangzeb%20a%20cruel%20ruler.%20During%20that%20era%2C%20power%20struggles%20were%20political%2C%20not%20religious.%20Aurangzeb's%20army%20had%20many%20Hindus%2C%20just%20as%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji's%20army%20had%20several%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%20He%20later%20retracted%20his%20remarks%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20was%20done%20and%20the%2017th%20C