usinessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-3-touchscreen-display-features-how-it-works-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20car's%20touchscreen%20suddenly%20became%20sluggish%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20unresponsive.%20The%20solution%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20reboot%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20felt%20more%20like%20troubleshooting%20a%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20time%2C%20a%20parking%20sensor%20update%20made%20my%20car%20think%20I%20was%20about%20to%20crash%20into%20invisible%20obstacles%2C%20setting%20off%20alarms%20and%20scaring%20me%20half%20to%20death%20while%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270eb9950-dda8-460d-ab6f-66ced8ac4967%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERepairs%20are%20expensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-order-canceled-cost-of-college-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20minimalist%20design%20is%20sleek%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20of%20its%20most%20striking%20features.%20The%20clean%2C%20button-free%20interior%2C%20dominated%20by%20a%20sleek%20touchscreen%2C%20makes%20the%20car%20feel%20futuristic%20and%20high-tech.%20Driving%20a%20Tesla%20often%20feels%20like%20operating%20a%20piece%20of%20advanced%20technology%20rather%20than%20just%20another%20vehicle.%20However%2C%20that%20same%20minimalist%20approach%20comes%20with%20drawbacks.%20With%20fewer%20physical%20controls%2C%20simple%20tasks%20like%20adjusting%20the%20climate%20or%20opening%20the%20glovebox%20require%20navigating%20through%20the%20touchscreen.%20And%20when%20things%20break%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20door%20handle%20or%20a%20sensor%20%E2%80%94%20repairs%20can%20be%20costly%20and%20time-consuming.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20third-party%20repair%20options.%20Traditional%20mechanics%20often%20won't%20touch%20Teslas%2C%20which%20means%20you%20have%20to%20go%20to%20Tesla's%20service%20centers.%20You%20could%20be%20waiting%20weeks%20for%20an%20appointment%20for%20a%20minor%20repair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20had%20an%20issue%20with%20my%20car's%20door%20handle%20(a%20problem%20frequently%20reported%20by%20Tesla%20owners%20in%20forums%20and%20service%20complaints)%2C%20I%20was%20told%20I%20would%20have%20to%20wait%20three%20weeks%20for%20a%20service%20appointment.%20I'm%20not%20alone%3A%20Model%20S%20and%20Model%20X%20owners%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20faced%20issues%20with%20retractable%20door%20handles%20failing%20due%20to%20motor%20or%20sensor%20malfunctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20cosmetic%20repairs%20can%20be%20expensive.%20Like%20many%20automakers%2C%20Tesla%20uses%20proprietary%20parts%2C%20but%20what%20makes%20repairs%20particularly%20expensive%20is%20the%20limited%20availability%20of%20third-party%20repair%20options.%20Many%20mechanics%20won't%20work%20on%20Teslas%2C%20and%20body%20shops%20often%20charge%20more%20due%20to%20the%20specialized%20materials%20and%20repair%20processes%20Tesla%20requires.%20Even%20minor%20cosmetic%20repairs%2C%20like%20fixing%20a%20dent%20or%20replacing%20a%20side%20mirror%2C%20can%20cost%20significantly%20more%20than%20on%20a%20traditional%20gas-powered%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298414aa9-8bdc-4ac3-894c-0ee50e1bf81d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20community%20feels%20intense%20to%20me%20at%20times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20buying%20a%20Tesla%20isn't%20just%20about%20getting%20a%20car%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20joining%20a%20movement%20centered%20on%20sustainability%2C%20cutting-edge%20technology%2C%20and%20a%20bold%20vision%20for%20the%20future%20of%20transportation.%20And%20while%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20enthusiastic%20and%20helpful%20Tesla%20owners%2C%20the%20community%20can%20sometimes%20feel%20a%20bit%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECriticizing%20Tesla%20in%20an%20online%20forum%20can%20invite%20a%20wave%20of%20die-hard%20defenders%20who%20refuse%20to%20acknowledge%20any%20flaw.%20When%20I%20shared%20my%20frustrations%20about%20my%20car's%20range%20in%20an%20online%20Tesla%20forum%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20backlash.%20Instead%20of%20sympathy%20or%20helpful%20advice%2C%20I%20got%20responses%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20you%20don't%20deserve%20a%20Tesla.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20clear%20that%20for%20some%20owners%2C%20any%20criticism%20of%20Tesla%20is%20off-limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there's%20also%20a%20genuine%20camaraderie%20among%20owners.%20At%20charging%20stations%2C%20I've%20had%20great%20conversations%20with%20fellow%20Tesla%20drivers%2C%20sharing%20road%20trip%20tips%2C%20commiserating%20over%20software%20bugs%2C%20and%20swapping%20stories%20about%20our%20favorite%20(and%20least%20favorite)%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7ab8c07-8e4c-4c59-9aad-4579faa57baf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20regret%20buying%20my%20Tesla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20headaches%2C%20I%20don't%20regret%20buying%20my%20Tesla.%20When%20it%20works%20as%20intended%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20magic.%20The%20instant%20torque%2C%20the%20smooth%20ride%2C%20the%20futuristic%20minimalism%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20hard%20to%20go%20back%20to%20a%20gas%20car%20after%20experiencing%20it.%20And%20yes%2C%20I%20love%20never%20having%20to%20stop%20at%20a%20gas%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWould%20I%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%3F%20That's%20a%20tougher%20question.%20The%20Tesla%20experience%20requires%20patience%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20deal%20with%20things%20that%20traditional%20car%20owners%20never%20have%20to%20consider.%20A%20Tesla%20might%20not%20be%20the%20right%20fit%20if%20you%20want%20a%20reliable%20car%20that%20gets%20you%20from%20point%20A%20to%20B%20without%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20the%20Tesla%20dream%20is%20both%20a%20blessing%20and%20a%20curse.%20I%20love%20my%20car%2C%20but%20I%20also%20brace%20myself%20whenever%20I%20update%20the%20software%2C%20take%20a%20road%20trip%2C%20or%20need%20a%20repair.%20Owning%20a%20Tesla%20is%20an%20adventure%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that's%20as%20thrilling%20as%20it%20is%20occasionally%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20author's%20issue%20with%20her%20car%20and%20general%20complaints.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fowning-tesla-what-no-one-tells-you-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742290501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d47310585f1dff88b237a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fowning-tesla-what-no-one-tells-you-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20have%20a%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20my%20Tesla.%20It's%20expensive%20to%20repair%20and%20I%20don't%20love%20the%20cult-like%20community%20around%20the%20brand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Bennett%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fowning-tesla-what-no-one-tells-you-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20Should%20Push%20Trump%20To%20Be%20Practical%20About%20Chabahar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConnectivity%20is%20crucial%20in%20our%20century...Armenia%20is%20deeply%20interested%20in%20advancing%20dialogue%20and%20developing%20cooperation%20in%20the%20International%20North-South%20Transport%20Corridor%20(INSTC)%20Project%20and%20the%20Chabahar%20Port%20Development%20Commission.%E2%80%9D%20These%20words%20were%20spoken%20by%20the%20Foreign%20Minister%20of%20Armenia%20Ararat%20Mirzoyan%20last%20week%20in%20New%20Delhi%20when%20he%20delivered%20the%2052nd%20Sapru%20House%20Lecture%20at%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20World%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmenia%20is%20a%20landlocked%20country%20and%20connectivity%20is%20an%20urgent%20issue.%20Given%20its%20location%20north%20of%20Iran%20and%20the%20need%20for%20sea%20access%20and%20access%20to%20the%20markets%20and%20goods%20of%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20further%20to%20Southeast%20Asia%20or%20even%20West%20Asia%2C%20connecting%20to%20the%20Chabahar%20port%20in%20Iran%20is%20imperative.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20country%20had%20signed%20on%20to%20the%20port%20project%20as%20early%20as%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Chabahar%20Is%20Important%20For%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmenia%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20understanding%20the%20benefits%20of%20being%20part%20of%20the%20Chabahar%20port%20project.%20Afghanistan%20is%20another%20country%20that%20has%20hugely%20benefited%20from%20the%20port.%20Possibly%2C%20it%20has%20been%20its%20greatest%20beneficiary%20and%20a%20raison%20d'%C3%AAtre%20for%20India%20developing%20the%20port.%20The%20route%20has%20enabled%20India%20to%20deliver%20crucial%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Afghanistan%20bypassing%20Pakistan%2C%20since%202012.%20In%20fact%2C%20India%20invested%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Zaranj-Delaram%20highway%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20with%20Zaranj%20close%20to%20the%20Iranian%20border%2C%20precisely%20to%20transport%20freight%20to%20Afghanistan%20from%20Chabahar.%20It%20has%20also%20invested%20in%20the%20Chabahar-Zahedan%20railway%2C%20though%20this%20project%20has%20moved%20at%20a%20painfully%20slow%20pace%20because%20of%20the%20sanctions%20the%20US%20imposed%20on%20Iran%20for%20its%20nuclear%20programme.%20Only%20the%20Chabahar%20port%2C%20being%20so%20important%20as%20it%20is%20for%20India's%20outreach%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20as%20also%20as%20a%20means%20to%20counter%20Pakistan's%20influence%20there%2C%20was%20spared%20from%20sanctions%20in%202012%20under%20Section%201244%20of%20the%20Iran%20Freedom%20and%20Counter-Proliferation%20Act%20(IFCA.%20Since%20then%2C%20successive%20US%20administrations%20have%20continued%20with%20the%20waiver%20granted%20to%20the%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20in%20office%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20has%20implemented%20a%20policy%20of%20%26quot%3Bmaximum%20pressure%26quot%3B%20on%20Iran%2C%20targeting%20its%20banking%20sector%20and%20other%20economic%20activities.%20This%20has%20also%20included%20reimposing%20sanctions%20on%20the%20Chabahar%20port%2C%20revoking%20all%20waivers.%20An%20executive%20order%20Trump%20issued%20called%20for%20modifying%20or%20rescinding%20sanctions%20waivers%2C%20%E2%80%9Cparticularly%20those%20that%20provide%20Iran%20with%20any%20degree%20of%20economic%20or%20financial%20relief%2C%20including%20those%20related%20to%20Iran's%20Chabahar%20port%20project%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Commitment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20make%20it%20very%20difficult%20for%20India%20to%20continue%20business%20through%20and%20related%20to%20the%20port.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20earmarked%20%24500%20million%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20port%2C%20with%20the%20work%20being%20done%20by%20India%20Ports%20Global%20Limited%20(IPGL).%20Even%20with%20all%20the%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20Iran%20and%20the%20port%20and%20the%20intensifying%20conflict%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%2C%20India%20signed%20a%2010-year%20contract%20in%20May%20last%20year%20for%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20Chabahar%20port.%20This%20move%20signalled%20an%20enormous%20resolve%2C%20though%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20responded%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BBroadly%2C%20you've%20heard%20us%20say%20this%20in%20a%20number%20of%20instances%2C%20that%20any%20entity%2C%20anyone%20considering%20business%20deals%20with%20Iran%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20risk%20that%20they%20are%20opening%20themselves%20up%20to%20and%20the%20potential%20risk%20of%20sanctions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Crucial%20Link%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChabahar%20is%20important%20for%20India%20for%20a%20number%20of%20reasons.%20It%20connects%20India%20to%20the%20markets%20and%20resources%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20Armenia%2C%20the%20Eurasian%20heartland%2C%20including%20those%20of%20the%20five%20Central%20Asian%20Republics%E2%80%94Kazakhstan%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20Tajikistan%2C%20Turkmenistan%2C%20and%20Uzbekistan%E2%80%94through%20the%20shortest%20routes%2C%20all%20bypassing%20the%20Suez%2C%20which%20has%20over%20the%20past%20years%20proven%20to%20be%20not%20as%20invincible%20as%20once%20believed.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20port%20is%20important%20to%20all%20these%20countries%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20port%20is%20also%20crucial%20to%20the%20multimodal%20trade%20corridor%2C%20the%20INSTC%2C%20which%20connects%20India%20to%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20and%20to%20Europe%20through%20its%20different%20branches%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20Central%20Asian%20countries.%20The%20corridor%20shortens%20transportation%20time%20by%2040%25%20and%20costs%20by%2030%25.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20first%20container%20train%20from%20India%20to%20Kazakhstan%20was%20launched%2C%20again%20travelling%20via%20Iran%2C%20Turkmenistan%20and%20Uzbekistan%2C%20shortening%20the%20transportation%20time%20to%2025%E2%80%9330%20days.%20Sanctions%20on%20the%20port%20would%20affect%20all%20these%20countries%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20close%20partners%20of%20the%20US%2C%20or%20with%20which%2C%20like%20the%20Central%20Asian%20countries%2C%20the%20US%20seeks%20steady%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20China%20Cloud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20connectivity%2C%20the%20Chabahar%20port%20is%20also%20strategically%20important%20for%20India.%20In%20this%20age%20of%20alternate%20and%20greater%20connectivity%20and%20trade%20and%20energy%20corridors%2C%20China%20and%20Turkey%20have%20already%20implemented%20their%20routes%E2%80%94China%20through%20its%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%20and%20Turkey%20through%20the%20Trans-Caspian%20International%20Transport%20Route%20(TITR)%2C%20aka%20the%20%E2%80%98Middle%20Corridor'.%20The%20Chabahar%20Port%20was%20also%20meant%20to%20counter%20the%20China-developed%20Gwadar%20Port%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20170%20kilometres%20away.%20The%20latter%20is%20part%20of%20Beijing's%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%2C%20a%20flagship%20project%20of%20the%20BRI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Beijing's%20rising%20influence%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20the%20Iranian%20port%20takes%20on%20more%20salience.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20INSTC%20and%20the%20other%20trade%20corridor%20envisaged%20to%20connect%20India%20to%20the%20Black%20Sea%20and%20Europe%20through%20Iran%2C%20Armenia%2C%20and%20Georgia%2C%20also%20offer%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20Middle%20Corridor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20chance%20for%20developing%20autonomy%20and%20diversification%20of%20trade%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Strategic%20Asset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20periphery%20in%20its%20neighbouring%20geographies%2C%20the%20Chabahar%20Port%20is%20a%20necessity%20and%20a%20strategic%20asset%20for%20India%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one.%20Therefore%2C%20like%20last%20year%2C%20the%20latest%20Union%20Budget%20has%20once%20again%20allocated%20Rs.%20100%20crore%20for%20Chabahar%20port%20for%202025-26.%20India%20has%20already%20invested%20approximately%20%24120%20million%20in%20Chabahar's%20development%20and%20extended%20Iran%20a%20%24250%20million%20credit%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20together%20with%20its%20partners%20and%20participating%20countries%20of%20the%20Chabahar%20port%20project%2C%20must%20impress%20upon%20the%20US%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20port%20and%20the%20sanctions%20waivers%20granted%20to%20it%20by%20successive%20American%20administrations.%20Trump%20must%20understand%20that%20the%20benefits%20accruing%20from%20the%20port's%20development%20to%20all%20these%20countries%20will%2C%20naturally%2C%20be%20beneficial%20to%20the%20US%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%C2%A0is%20a%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742290440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F05m6s35o_chabahar-port-_625x300_13_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-should-press-trump-to-be-practical-about-chabahar-7950147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Beijing's%20rising%20influence%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20the%20Iranian%20port%20takes%20on%20salience%20and%20shouldn't%20become%20a%20casualty%20of%20Trump's%20'Maximum%20Pressure'%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-should-press-trump-to-be-practical-about-chabahar-7950147%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Catalan%20Political%20Scandal%20Drama%20%E2%80%98Our%20Father%2C%20Our%20President%E2%80%99%20Scooped%20By%20Filmax%20Ahead%20of%20Malaga%E2%80%99s%20Spanish%20Screenings%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742290363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FOur-Father-Our-President.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236339206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Filmax%20has%20secured%20international%20rights%20to%20%E2%80%9COur%20Father%2C%20Our%20President%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20latest%20film%20from%20celebrated%20Catalan%20filmmaker%20Manel%20Huerga%20(%E2%80%9CSalvador%20(Puig%20Antich)%E2%80%9D).%20The%20Barcelona-based%20sales%20company%20will%20host%20a%20market%20screening%20for%20the%20feature%20at%20the%20upcoming%20Spanish%20Screenings%20at%20the%20Malaga%20Film%20Festival.%20With%20his%20latest%20political%20drama%2C%20Hu