20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0When%20the%20media%20asked%20him%20about%20not%20getting%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20democratic%20structure%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20should%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20speak%2C%20but%20they%20won't%20let%20us.%20This%20is%20new%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20speech%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20praised%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20administration%20for%20successfully%20hosting%20the%20Kumbh%2C%20which%20saw%20a%20massive%20footfall%20of%20over%2060%20crore.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20public%20and%20administration%20for%20the%20successful%20organisation%20of%20the%20Mahakumbh.%20The%20success%20of%20the%20Mahakumbh%20is%20the%20result%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20various%20people.%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20everyone%3A%20the%20country's%20devotees%2C%20the%20public%20of%20UP%2C%20especially%20the%20people%20of%20Prayagraj.%20We%20all%20know%20that%20strenuous%20efforts%20took%20place%20to%20bring%20Ganga%20to%20earth%3B%20similar%20efforts%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20hold%20the%20grand%20Mahakumbh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20has%20witnessed%20the%20great%20glory%20of%20Bharat%20through%20the%20Mahakumbh.%20This%20is%20because%20of%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20country's%20people.%20This%20Mahakumbh%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%2C%20for%20the%20determination%20of%20the%20people.%20In%20this%20Mahakumbh%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20greatness%20of%20the%20awakening%20of%20our%20national%20consciousness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20grand%20event's%20success%20had%20silenced%20doubts%20and%20fears%20raised%20by%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20critics%26quot%3B%20about%20India's%20capabilities.%20He%20said%20the%20gathering%20was%20a%20powerful%20demonstration%20of%20the%20nation's%20potential%20and%20resolve.%20%26quot%3BWe%20felt%20the%20nation's%20preparations%20for%20the%20next%201%2C000%20years%20during%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20ceremony%2C%20and%20today%2C%20just%20one%20year%20later%2C%20the%20organisation%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20reinforces%20that%20same%20vision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20life%20of%20any%20nation%2C%20there%20are%20events%20that%20become%20part%20of%20its%20history%2C%20transcending%20time%20and%20becoming%20an%20example%20for%20the%20generations%20to%20come.%20The%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20one%20such%20event%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%2C%20underscoring%20the%20significance%20of%20such%20national%20milestones%20in%20strengthening%20the%20collective%20spirit%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20grandeur%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20awakening%20of%20our%20national%20consciousness%2C%20and%20it%20stands%20as%20a%20powerful%20reply%20to%20those%20who%20doubt%20our%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20Opposition%20must%20have%20been%20allowed%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20Kumbh.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Prime%20Minister)%20was%20speaking%20optimistically%20on%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%20The%20Opposition%20also%20should%20have%20been%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20present%20their%20point%20because%20the%20Opposition%20also%20has%20sentiments%20towards%20it%20and%20they%20should%20not%20have%20any%20problem%20if%20we%20expressed%20ourselves.%20The%20Opposition%20should%20have%20also%20been%20allowed%20to%20speak%20for%20two%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2044-day%20religious%20gathering%20at%20Prayagraj%20drew%20crores%20of%20pilgrims%20and%20tourists%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20a%20tragic%20event%20during%20the%20event%20was%20a%20stampede%20near%20the%20Sangam%20-%20the%20confluence%20of%2