0to%20the%20defense%20budgets%20of%20Israel%20and%20South%20Korea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20did%20point%20out%20that%20this%20was%20considerably%20less%20than%20the%20current%20wartime%20expenditures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20deter%20another%20Russian%20attack%2C%20Ukraine%20would%20need%20to%20lay%20extensive%20defensive%20lines%20of%20mines%2C%20trenches%2C%20and%20artillery%2C%20and%20guard%20them%20with%20enough%20troops%20to%20slow%20down%20an%20assault%20force%20so%20it%20could%20rush%20more%20resources%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20also%20hit%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-offensive-ukraine-glide-bombs-nato-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccessful%20mix%20of%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20glide%20bombs%20and%20exploding%20drones%20to%20advance%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20could%20use%20a%20spell%20of%20months%20to%20rebuild%20its%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpurling%20said%20that%20the%20shorter%20and%20less%20jagged%20a%20front%20line%20is%2C%20the%20easier%20it%20is%20to%20defend%2C%20and%20Ukraine%20would%20be%20seeking%20to%20draw%20the%20line%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20geographical%20features%20that%20gives%20its%20defenders%20an%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDone%20properly%2C%20it's%20a%20complex%20undertaking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20ISW%20called%20for%20the%20US%20to%20back%20Ukraine%20in%20pushing%20back%20Russian%20forces%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20in%20establishing%20a%20front%20line%20along%20positions%20that%20can%20be%20more%20easily%20defended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20ceasefire%20along%20more%20defensible%20positions%20would%20also%20place%20Russian%20forces%20in%20a%20more%20disadvantaged%20position%20for%20renewed%20offensive%20operations%2C%20making%20future%20Russian%20aggression%20less%20likely%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22310dcf4e-1e45-4317-9f49-5fd5cd4