tups%2C%20including%20rocket%20propulsion%20provider%20Ursa%20Major%20and%20hypersonic%20aircraft%20developer%20Hermeus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20main%20focus%20is%20on%20identifying%20teams%20with%20outstanding%20technical%20and%20engineering%20talent%20and%20experience%20that%20have%20developed%20a%20disruptive%20vision%20and%20strategy%20with%20an%20actionable%20plan%20to%20build%20a%20scalable%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Ateya%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESteve%20Bowsher%2C%20In-Q-Tel%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Bowsher%20of%20In-Q-Tel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d88c1e69253ccddf997efb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteve%20Bowsher%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20In-Q-Tel.%3Cp%3EIn-Q-Tel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Menlo%20Park%2C%20California%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENotable%20investments%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Palantir%2C%20Databricks%2C%20MongoDB%2C%20Anaconda%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20he's%20on%20the%20list%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20head%20of%20investment%20strategy%20(and%20later%20President%20and%20CEO)%20of%20In-Q-Tel%2C%20the%20CIA's%20venture%20capital%20fund%2C%20Bowsher%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20helped%20create%20the%20entire%20defense%20tech%20startup%20ecosystem.%20He%20made%20an%20early%20bet%20on%20Palantir%2C%20blowing%20the%20doors%20open%20for%20Silicon%20Valley%20techies%20to%20go%20after%20federal%20contracts.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20conventional%20wisdom%20in%20venture%20capital%20was%20that%20there%20was%20no%20point%20in%20trying%20to%20sell%20to%20the%20government%3B%20too%20slow%2C%20too%20much%20red%20tape%2C%20too%20much%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20many%20reference%20calls%20I%20did%20for%20venture%20capitalists%20between%202006%20and%202012%20or%20so%20who%20were%20thi