C%22%3EDeliverr%3C%2Fa%3E%20cofounder%20and%20former%20Shopify%20vice%20president%2C%20launched%20a%20new%20startup%20called%20Augment%20out%20of%20stealth%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAugment%20is%20building%20an%20AI%20assistant%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-react-to-tariffs-ryan-peterson-flexport-logistics-manufacturing-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elogistics%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20has%20raised%20%2425%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%2C%20led%20by%208VC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20assistant%2C%20called%20Augie%2C%20can%20respond%20to%20emails%20and%20Slack%20messages%2C%20make%20and%20receive%20phone%20calls%2C%20manage%20workflows%2C%20and%20perform%20other%20routine%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20text%20them%2C%20you%20can%20email%20them%2C%20you%20can%20message%20them%20on%20Slack.%20You%20can%20assign%20work%20to%20them%2C%20and%20they%20go%20about%20doing%20their%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Abbott%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbott%20said%20the%20idea%20for%20Augment%20came%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20on%20an%20industry%20he%20knows%20well.%20He%20cofounded%20Deliverr%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20built%20software%20to%20enable%20quick%20shipping%2C%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-plans-billion-acquisition-of-deliverr-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShopify%20for%20%242.1%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-logistics-deliverr-sale-flexport-layoffs-crisis-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShopify%20sold%20Deliverr%3C%2Fa%3E%20(and%20the%20rest%20of%20its%20logistics%20business)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflexport-layoffs-end-chaos-ex-deliverr-shopify-workers-compensation-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlexport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Abbott%20spent%20just%20under%20a%20year%20at%20Flexport%20before%20starting%20to%20build%20Augment%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAugment%20will%20start%20in%20trucking%2C%20targeting%20shippers%2C%20brokers%2C%20and%20trucking%20companies%20before%20expanding%20to%20the%20larger%20logistics%20industry.%20Abbott%20said%20that%20Augie%20has%20been%20used%20in%20businesses%20that%20collectively%20have%20%2420%20billion%20of%20freight%20under%20management.%20Its%20early%20customers%20include%20Austin-based%20brokerage%20Arrive%20Logistics%20and%20third-party%20logistics%20provider%20NFI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrucking%20is%20a%20nearly%20trillion-dollar%20industry%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20trucking%20companies%20serve%20as%20the%20connective%20tissue%20for%20commerce%2C%20transporting%20shipments%20between%20warehouses%2C%20ports%2C%20and%20retail%20stores.%20The%20last%20three%20years%20have%20been%20difficult%20for%20this%20industry%20as%20it's%20endured%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-freight-recession-transportation-stocks-dow-jbhunt-ups-fedex-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongest%20recessions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20history.%20This%20means%20transportation%20companies%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20alleviate%20pressure%20on%20their%20margins%2C%20Abbott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20very%20fragmented%20industry.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20trucking%20companies%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20no%20one%20standard%20system%20they%20all%20use%20to%20conduct%20business%2C%20besides%20email.%20Abbott%20said%20that%20when%20shadowing%20people%20working%20in%20this%20space%2C%20he%20saw%20that%20employees%20receive%20as%20many%20as%20500%20to%20600%20emails%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20shipper%20has%20to%20book%20a%20truck%2C%20they%20email%20maybe%20four%20or%20five%20brokers%2C%26quot%3B%20Abbott%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20broker%20responds%2C%20then%20they%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20and%20negotiate%20on%20a%20bid.%20Then%20the%20broker%20takes%20that%20and%20emails%2010%20or%2015%20trucking%20companies%2C%20then%20they%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20shows%20a%20Slack%20workspace%20working%20with%20Augie%2C%20an%20AI%20assitant%20that%20can%20make%20phone%20calls%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d8743469253ccddf997999%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAugie%20can%20chat%20with%20employees%20in%20Slack%20and%20make%20phone%20calls%20on%20their%20behalf.%3Cp%3EAugment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c5345aa-0b62-44be-a366-8fc62942e1e8%5C%22%3E'Logistics%20is%20not%20solved'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbbott%20said%20his%20time%20at%20Shopify%20gave%20him%20an%20%26quot%3Beven%20stronger%20feel%20of%20the%20problems%26quot%3B%20faced%20by%20the%20millions%20of%20merchants%20using%20the%20e-commerce%20platform.%20Getting%20their%20products%20to%20customers%20remains%20one%20of%20merchants'%20biggest%20challenges%20and%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20time%20at%20Flexport%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20showed%20how%20%26quot%3Bmessy%26quot%3B%20global%20trade%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20reinforced%20for%20me%20that%20one%2C%20logistics%20is%20not%20solved.%20Two%2C%20it's%20crucially%20important.%20And%20three%2C%20I%20think%20AI%20is%20the%20answer%20to%20these%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAugie%20runs%20on%20different%20large%20language%20models%20depending%20on%20the%20scenario%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-computer-use-ai-explainer-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F